MtgDB,is,a,simple,open,source,database,API,for,the,Magic,The,Gathering,MTG,card,game,It,allows,users,to,copy,and,sync,their,own,MTG,databases,Although,MtgDB,does,support,basic,filtering,it,is,not,designed,as,a,full,search,API,All,of,the,information,provided,by,the,API,is,copyrighted,by,Wizards,of,the,Coast,the,company,that,owns,MTG,This,API,is,not,affiliated,with,Wizards,of,the,Coast,in,any,way